title: Seirei Gensouki
synopsis: Amakawa Haruto is a young man who died before reuniting with his childhood friend who disappeared five years ago. Rio is a boy living in the slums who wants revenge for his mother who was murdered in front of him when he was five years old. Earth and another world. Two people with completely different backgrounds and values. For some reason, the memories and personality of Haruto who should've died is resurrected in Rio's body. As the two are confused over their memories and personalities fusing together, Rio decides to live in this new world. Along with Haruto's memories, Rio awakens an unknown "special power," and it seems that if he uses it well, he can live a better life. But before that, Rio encounters a kidnapping that turns out to be of a princess of the Bertram Kingdom that he lives in. After saving the princess, Rio is given a scholarship at the Royal Academy, a school for the rich and powerful. Being a poor orphan in a school of nobles turns out to be an extremely detestable place to be. (Source: MU)

Then, the moment it was declared that it's plagiarized, the plagiarized work changed form into a homage. The line between doing plagiarism and doing a homage seems ambiguous, and the truth is that that line doesn't exist anywhere. It holds true even when the role is reversed. A homage holds a great risk of becoming plagiarism. The lyrics to this song pays homage to Ozaki Housai's haiku and his final years of life. (Source: YouTube)

title: Puraore! Pride of Orange
synopsis: The story takes place in Nikko city, Tochigi Prefecture, where girls aim for the top of the world through ice hockey. Local junior high school student Manaka and her younger sister Ayaka, whom she forcibly invited, hit the gate of first-hand experience with ice hockey, held by the Nikko-based team Dream Monkeys. The two are joined by their childhood friends Kaoruko and Mami. As the girls practice, they become fascinated with ice hockey and eventually join the team. (Source: MAL News)

title: Selection Project
synopsis: Held every summer, the national show "Selection Project" is the biggest gateway for girls who strive to be idols, and the place where the legendary idol Akari Amazawa was born. Suzune Miyama is also one who has longed for such a dream stage. Having been sick since childhood, she listened to the song of the light many times in her bed in the hospital room. Akari's singing voice gave her a lot of smiles and courage, inspiring Suzune to follow in her footsteps. In her last summer of junior high school, Suzune decides to challenge the 7th annual Selection Project to make her dream come true. The girls who challenge Selection all have strong feelings that are second to none, accumulated efforts, and extraordinary charm. Only nine stars are selected from among the thousands of candidates. Now, the hot and harsh "Audition Battle" of the  girls begins to make their dreams come true. (Source: MAL News)

title: Kyuukyoku Shinka shita Full Dive RPG ga Genjitsu yori mo Kusoge Dattara
synopsis: In an unexpected turn of events, dull high school student Hiro Yuuki obtains the full dive role-playing game Kiwame Quest. Created by the best of technology, the game claims to take "reality to its extremes," from stunning graphics, NPCs' behavior, to the scent of vegetation, and even the sensation of wind brushing against the skin—everything was the result of an ultimate workmanship. Except, the game is a little too realistic and messy to clear. Kiwame Quest features over ten quadrillion flags and reflects the players' real-life physical abilities in the game. Being hit in the game also hurts in real life and slash wounds take days to heal. The only reward here is the sense of accomplishment. Conquer the most stressful game in history that can't be played casually! (Source: MAL News)

details.Synonyms: What If the Ultimately Evolved Full Dive RPG was a Crappier Game than Reality

title: Guodong Baobei
synopsis: There is a saying in the village that if anyone does not want to exercise and be lazy all day, they will attract terrible monsters. However, in the hearts of the children in the village, they all think that this is just a distant legend, and no one takes that legend seriously. Until one day, Niuniu made a peculiar smell because of his laziness, and attracted the bad witch who accidentally discovered this magical village while refining witchcraft. The bad witch who lives in the pumpkin castle covets the magical physique of the jelly baby. She wants to catch and eat them to restore her lost youth. In order to find the jelly village and grab the jelly baby, the yay witch even stretched her claws towards The Milk River where the Jelly babies depend for survival. In order not to allow the witches and witches to easily find the Jelly Village, the Jelly babies have gone through hardships to give the Milk River a life. They once again crushed the witch’s evil conspiracy. The bad witch who has repeatedly failed, ah, witch-qi fainted, and actually used his remaining health and youth to exchange three terrible magic from the devil... However, the ah ah witch who used the new magic still failed to catch the jelly baby as he wished, and instead made himself aging. Just when the old, ugly, frustrated ah ah witch completely lost fighting spirit and hope, annoyed and desperate, jelly The baby began to sympathize with this poor and hateful old opponent. They tried their best to help her defeat her own demons, and let Yeah Wu understand: The secret of eternal youth is to maintain a healthy mind. You should drink more milk and exercise. . Yeah, the witch finally made up his mind, broke the contract with the devil, and returned the magic to the devil. From then on, ya ya wu lived near the lower reaches of the Milk River, and with the help of the river water and appropriate exercises to retrieve the lost youth little by little, ya ya witch no longer dared to catch the jelly baby, because as long as she has a bad mind, she finally got it. Youth will be lost again.(translated from baidu baike)

title: Guodong San Jianke
synopsis: This is a funny fairy tale that eliminates evil and punishes rape. The characters in the story are all cute fruits, and all animations are made in three dimensions. The "Jelly Three Musketeers" are three students in the Jelly Martial Arts Academy. The three come from completely different family backgrounds: Orange Liuxiang comes from a third-rate swordsman's family; Pineapple Chuuxue comes from an ordinary family of ordinary people; Lu Xiaoguo is proud of his family. The three of them want to be the pillars of the country; one wants to be a millionaire; the other wants to have a lot of food that can never be eaten. In the process of practicing martial arts, the three people made a lot of jokes. The teacher was angry and loving to them. After hard training, the three people finally passed the various difficult tests and tests of the college teacher, and they were ready to go down the mountain! The opponents of the "Jelly Three Musketeers" are the four big thieves, "Thief Brows, Rat Eyes," "Recognize Thieves as Father", "Lesbian Ministers" and "World Without Thieves". Once again failed. Finally, the four evil thieves became angry and gathered together and vowed to defeat the Jelly Three Musketeers. And they have a bigger conspiracy, which is to sell the country's border defense maps in exchange for huge rewards from the enemy country. For the sake of national safety, the Jelly Three Musketeers certainly stepped forward and fought against the four big thieves. From Shanzhai Dou to the capital, and from the capital to the frontier, the three finally defeated the four evil thieves and became the national heroes. (translated from baidu baike)

title: Guo Bao Tegong
synopsis: The jelly martial arts academy was originally a harmonious place, where the jelly people study and play happily. Unexpectedly, one day an uninvited guest came—thug eyebrow and mouse eye, he was one of the four evil thieves. Disturbed the peace in the college. In order to maintain peace, the abbot drove Ye Yan and Shangguan Ziyi to the Tianshan Mountains. And he gave the three swords left by the master to Orange Liuxiang, Pineapple Chuuxue and Lu Xiaoguo. When the Guobao Special Attacks heard that the big demon Dongfang Qiufei and the four evil thieves had poisoned the Seven Colored Lotus and harmed the villagers, they made up their minds to kill the people. Unexpectedly, this was the trick of Xiao Guoding: He sent some fruit villagers to spread rumors, saying that Dongfang Qiu had opened a fruit processing factory, which was the hell of the fruit, and let them fight and lose both. Later, a lawsuit proved the innocence of Dongfang Qiu and the four evil thieves. Xiao Guoding took four runners (papaya boy, grape boy, Wu Xing'er and blueberry village chief) to design and capture the five drivers of Guoyuan Tianzun (Yeyan, Promise, Hero, Crazy Qingyang, Tianshan Guomao), And driving Guoyuan Tianzun to fight with Guobao Special Attack on the seventh floor of Huaguo Mountain. The seventh floor of Huaguo Mountain is not a place where everyone can go up. It is an inverted triangle. The runners headed by Xiao Guoding and the Guobao special attackers headed by Orange Liuxiang (Orange Liuxiang, Pineapple Blistering Snow, Lu Xiaoguo, Pineapple Xiaowei, Shangguan Ziyi, Lihua Shi and Huaruyi) summoned Guobao on the seventh floor. Mecha makes the seventh layer very unstable. For the sake of the fruit world and to support the seventh floor of Huaguo Mountain, the Devil King (Eastern Defeat and the Four Great Thieves) drained the volcanic energy at all costs, and finally activated the source of life. And the seventh floor is another fierce war. Guobao Ares attacked the opponent separately. At first, they had the upper hand, but later Li Huashi and Pineapple Xiaowei were trampled to death. Lu Xiaoguo and Hua Ruyi also died on the steps due to the failure of the double-sword attack on the wall. Shangguan Ziyi sacrificed to save the orange fragrance, and Pineapple Blowing Snow Also died because of a failed sneak attack. Orange Liuxiang opened up the source of life for the fruit world, and ultimately died. Originally Xiao Guoding was about to win, but the Guobao special attackers with a heart of justice were resurrected, and the mechas were all upgraded with gold. He could have defeated his opponent, but when Orange Liuxiang learned that the Devil King's energy was about to run out, he dropped his weapon and led the Guobao Special Attacks to take over the seventh floor. Because Xiao Guoding has never been the protagonist of a good person, he has rescued the seven-color lotus, the fruit world is reborn, and the fruits are reunited!(translated from baidu baike)

title: For The Win
synopsis: Official music video for Aqua Minato's second original song. In her words, it's dedicated to "all gamers of the world", and is "a cheering song for "League of Legends 2020 World Championship"".

title: Guo Bao Tegong 2
synopsis: After successfully saving the fruit world, the fruits celebrated their victory in the Huaguoshan chorus, and unexpectedly caused the collapse of the seventh layer, hurting the Seven Color Lotus. In order to rescue Cailian, Dongfang Qiu was accidentally bewitched and used by outsiders. He accepted the ninjutsu of the human world, but he also became an accomplice of the fruit abductors. The abbot and Grandma Guo went up the mountain to visit the East for defeat, and they unintentionally saw the clues. When the Three Musketeers arrived, the abbot and Grandma Guo, in order to preserve their strength, pretended to be mad and stupid, and the other swindled to death. They also made a ruthless move to knock the Three Musketeers off the cliff, and talked crazy, causing everyone to misunderstand the Three Musketeers. The Three Musketeers no longer have a foothold, and must go far away to avoid the persecution of the East for defeat. With the help of Xiao Guoding, the Three Musketeers recovered their lives, regaining their fighting spirit and vowing to find out the truth. Everyone did their best and went through many sufferings, and the mecha was reborn under the baptism of lotus beads. The three of them continue to improve themselves, acquire new skills and nirvana, and the opponent has also been strengthened and upgraded weapons. In addition to those ninjutsu, the three of them have fallen into bitter battles many times. The Three Musketeers repeatedly defeated and fought, and grew up in failure. Everyone met in Huaguo Mountain and ushered in the ultimate battle with the East for defeat .(translated from baidu baike)

title: Guo Bao Tegong 3
synopsis: The seven-color lotus on the seventh floor of Huaguo Mountain withered mysteriously and continuously released bad fruit factors. It turned out to be the conspiracy of the treacherous Tortoise Grandpa. Pineapple Blowing Snow wanted to stop the incident from being involved in the vortex of time and space and traveled with the Tortoise Grandpa to the war-torn Three Kingdoms. era. Pineapple Chuuxue is revered as the emperor who saves the world and saves the people because of the yellow lotus with the seven-color lotus. He is incarnate as the historical figure Benevolent Zhu Xuande (Liu Bei). During this period, he met the brave Yide (Zhang Fei, Lu Xiaoguo ancestor), and later met the loyal and righteous Yunchang (Guan Yu, the ancestor of Orange Liuxiang), the three met late, and then they became three brothers in Taoyuan. In order to quell the long-standing chaos of war, he vowed to ascend to the seventh floor of Huaguo Mountain to defeat the traitorous Dongfang Qiong and save the people of the world from the deep waters. Just as the forces of the Three Kingdoms were about to unify, the gears of fate turned again, and the pineapple blowing snow once again triggered a space-time vortex, crossing into the human world.(translated from baidu baike)

title: Ai-mai Chocolate
synopsis: Official music video for Watame Tsunomaki's first full original song.

title: Guo Bao Tegong 4 Zhi Kai Zhi Hun
synopsis: Among the fruit arena, martial arts is the most sought after! Among them, the Orthodox Church founded by Guobao heroes orange Liuxiang, pineapple blowing snow, and Lu Xiaoguo is the most eye-catching. The three are known as the Three Musketeers of the Fruit Treasures. But at the celebration of the third anniversary of the Orthodox Church, the four great thieves turned out to defeat the Three Musketeers, changed the Orthodox Church into a perverted religion, eliminated other sects, arrested villagers, and disturbed the people. In order to rescue the people and recreate the Orthodox Church, with the help of the quaint people in the world, the Three Musketeers defeated the monsters and got upgraded mechas. They set off to the location of the four evil thieves. On the way, they also met with Shangguan Ziyi and Xiao Guoding. , Ye Yan and others have experienced a period of laughter and curse, bloody and funny stories. And the hard fights again and again are growth again and again. With the heart of perseverance and never giving up, the Three Musketeers finally defeated the four evil thieves and returned to the top. When the Three Musketeers thought that the crisis was over, they never thought that the master behind the four evil thieves would make Dongfang Qiu defeat appear! Faced with the Eastern Seeking Defeat and the Four Great Thieves who are trying to subvert the fruit arena, the Three Musketeers, Crazy Qingyang and others fought a earth-shattering battle with them at the lotus place of the Seven Realms Mountain, which is about the survival of the fruit world. In the end, the Three Musketeers and others died with Dongfang Qiu and the four evil thieves, guarding the fruit world with their lives.(translated from baidu baike)

title: Guo Bao Tegong Zhi Shuiguo Da Taowang
synopsis: Orange Liuxiang, from the home of a third-rate swordsman, is a bit dull, extremely insensitive to love, and has poor luck, but still has a righteous heart. As the leader of the Three Musketeers, he has high ambitions and wants to become a talented person who has made great contributions to the motherland like Zhang Sanfeng. In "Guobao Special Attack: Fruit Escape", the brain waves of orange Liuxiang will interact with a critically ill young boy by chance in a fruit supermarket. At this time, many little mice are always running around in all corners of the supermarket, making rustling noises from time to time, making people feel restless and irritable when listening, and they always make the food in the supermarket messy, which is really amazing. Detested. It just so happened that the little boy interacted with the brain waves of Orange Liuxiang, and he wanted to extend justice and kill the people. Orange Liuxiang took this as an opportunity to interact with the little boy in the supermarket with the hateful little mice. Fierce fight(translated from baidu baike)

title: Bai Bian Ji Shou Zhi Luo Luo Lixian Ji
synopsis: The 11-year-old "Lolo" is a genius game master, best at playing a 3D computer game called "King of Machines". This is a game with robots competing for supremacy against each other as a background game. Lolo has won the competition excellence award of this game many times. However, on a night of thunder and lightning, Lolo was no longer a bystander in this war. A strange beam of lightning injected powerful energy into Lolo’s computer and dragged him from the real world into the virtual world of the "War King" Inside, the story unfolds. (translated from baidu baike)

details.Japanese: 百变机兽之洛洛历险记

title: Wu Zhan Dao
synopsis: "Wu Zhan Dao" tells the story of a game master boy, Lolo, who happened to enter the virtual 3D game by chance-a world of robots where the weak and strong. He drives the brave robots of the locomotive family all the way through and becomes the king of robots in the game world. During the entire battle, Luo Luo understood the same truth as Hu Shatian who was betrayed by the Blue Devil Scorpion, "in addition to victory and defeat, there are feelings."(translated from baidu baike)

title: Di Bi Gou
synopsis: Therefore, many mysterious guests from different planets were gathered. There are humorous magicians, star rock bands, romantic and cute explorers, and noble and elegant cat queens. They are all attracted by this fascinating planet. But behind these travelers are hidden secrets. What is their ultimate purpose in coming to Dibi Star? The lively and lovely Adi will take everyone to find the truth behind the story. Countless treasures are buried under the palace.(translated from baidu baike)

title: Yuzhou Xing Shen
synopsis: In 2401, the teenagers Di Lu, Yaoyao and Xiao An discovered a mysterious object from the core of the Milky Way Galaxy during an outing. The star of the galaxy contains an unsolved mystery in the universe. The curious Dilu decided to embark on a journey in the universe with two good friends to solve this ultimate secret. With the help of spaceship pilot Lily, they began to explore the nine planets of the solar system. With the help of the universe star gods, relying on courage and wisdom, they finally solved the unknown mystery of the Milky Way star. (translated from baidu baike)

title: Chao Shou Wuzhuang Zhi Renzhe Wudi
synopsis: In a holy war 100,000 years ago, Hades and Snow Emperor were sealed one after another, and the Seven Universes ushered in 100,000 years of peace. Today, one hundred thousand years later, Pluto will wake up in seven days. At that time, the seven parallel universes will usher in a doomsday catastrophe. In order to prevent this catastrophe, the five beast warriors full of conviction set foot on the road to destroy the Hades without hesitation. It’s a pity that when they are about to destroy Pluto, it is also the moment when Pluto fully awakens.(translated from baidu baike)

title: Chao Shou Wuzhuang Zhi Yongzhe Wu Ju
synopsis: The Super Beast team was beaten by Hades into the Xuanming black hole space that sealed the Snow Emperor. In adversity, everyone met Xuehuang and others, and everyone rushed out of the Xuanming black hole. Pluto and Snow Emperor are in a fierce battle. When they are about to die together, several super beast warriors are involved in the wormhole and unexpectedly return to one hundred thousand years ago. They are facing their unknown past. , The belief of being super beast warriors gradually collapsed, they must regain their belief and realize their true mission (translated from baidu baike)

title: Gangtie Feilong
synopsis: In 2026, the earth's environment will deteriorate, and mankind will fall into a major ecological crisis. The Forestry Bureau, Land and Resources Bureau and other relevant departments attach great importance to them. Leading cadres responded actively and received instructions from their superiors. The environmental protection base decided to select a group of outstanding members to form the Feilong environmental protection team to investigate the causes of the global environmental crisis and find ways to prevent further deterioration of the environment. The team consists of five young people: Captain Flaming, Think Tank Deep Blue, Sports Master Artest, Girl Xiaoxin and Computer Genius Xiaoxing. They have gone through many difficulties and dangers, and prevented the conspiracy of the evil scientist "Mozun" behind the scenes and restored the ecological environment to normal. The earth returned to its former calm, and the Feilong environmental protection team returned to the base and continued to work hard to protect the earth's ecological environment.(translated from douban)

title: Gangtie Feilong (movie)
synopsis: The story tells that mysterious aliens began to infiltrate the world in an attempt to invade the earth. The genius scientist Dr. J sounded the alarm, but few believers. Only the world police officer Ito believed this and organized the secret force "Iron Flying Dragon". ". The five selected as members are problem children from all over the world. Although they have their own problems, they have outstanding abilities. They will ride on the "super deformed metal" armor developed by Dr. J, as well as huge robots and dive into the world Of aliens have a magnificent battle.(translated from baidu baike)

title: Gangtie Feilong Zhi Zaijian Ao Te Man
synopsis: To protect the earth and maintain peace, Ultraman used to be a god-like existence to the people on earth, but in recent decades, he has disappeared and disappeared into a mystery... Then he was replaced by the Iron Dragon Elite Team—— Affiliated to the GSB Earth Security Organization. And GSB has recently received continuous reports of earth energy anomalies, and huge disasters have occurred around the world. The GSB organization sent a steel flying dragon to find out the cause of the energy anomaly, but it was accidentally discovered that the incident was related to Ultraman... The unexpected encounter between the old and new generations of the guardians of the earth has become a life-and-death rivalry. In the end, was this an accident or a conspiracy, who saw the final truth?(translated from douban)

details.Japanese: 钢铁飞龙之再见奥特曼

title: Gangtie Feilong Zhi Ao Te Man Jueqi
synopsis: The creation spar crisis is on the verge. In order to prevent the destruction of the earth, Altman chose Lele, a seemingly ordinary boy, as his human body. Faced with numerous challenges, the originally naughty kid was guided by Altman. , Became the key figure to save the earth, and the secret of Ultraman's superpowers was gradually revealed... (translated from douban)

details.Japanese: 钢铁飞龙之奥特曼崛起

title: Gangtie Feilong 3 Shanhai Shenshou Lu
synopsis: In the future, the evil Skynet will lead the cosmic army to rule the earth, and Situ Le will lead mankind to resist tenaciously, and Skynet's troops will be retreating steadily. In order to reverse the situation, Skynet sent a large number of monsters back in time, vowing to kill Situ Le in his childhood. After repeated failures, Skynet decided to go back to clean up Situ Le and his party. Skynet set a trap to send Situ Le and the Iron Flying Dragon into the different world in the "Shan Hai Jing", and drove the mechanical mountain and sea monster built by hand to launch a fierce attack on Situ Le and them. When they were isolated and helpless, Situ Le and Iron Flying Dragon discovered a mysterious power from the broken pages of "Shan Hai Jing", and with the help of this power, they summoned a brand new mountain and sea monster mech. Facing the dangerous world of mountains and seas, Situ Le and Steel Flying Dragon drove a brand-new mythical beast mech, repelling Skynet's monsters time and time again, and embarked on a long way home. In the battle between Lele and Fusang, a character very similar to Ding Jiayi appeared in the real world. In a critical situation, Lele was rescued and a certain energy was triggered to successfully integrate the five steel flying dragon robots. While defeating Fusang, it also left suspense for the development of the second half of the story.(translated from douban)

title: Gangtie Feilong 2 Zhi Ao Te Man Liliang
synopsis: "Gangtie Feilong 2" is about aliens who were defeated or expelled from the earth by Ultraman and invaded again. Some have their wings hardened and come back to find Altman to seek revenge, some have escaped from prison to avenge the earth, and some come to brush their presence. These aliens have all kinds of abilities, and the earth is in crisis again. At the critical moment, the steel flying dragon team came forward and fought with the returning Ultraman to protect the safety of the earth.

title: Gangtie Feilong 2 Long Hun Juexing
synopsis: The story is based on the ordinary school life of Little Fatty Lele, telling the story of the steel flying dragon-Blazing Flame, Deep Blue, Iron Fist, Maggie, and Xiaoxing five warriors from the future world, guiding and leading Lele to defeat the monsters time and time again. In the process, the story that accompanies him to grow into a future hero. In addition to the passion and adventure elements in the whole film, there will also be the feelings of the little protagonist after the adventure, so that the children can learn to grow in the hero.(translated from douban)
